    "The selection is passed as arguments (\"$@\", \"$1\"). Also available: $DIRNEX_CURRENT_DIR, $DIRNEX_OTHER_DIR, $DIRNEX_SELECTED_PATHS.": {
      "comment": "Scripts organizer help text; the $-tokens are literal shell variables and stay untranslated.",
